OL,3,CTaxpayer cost of Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FIn a recent finance report, Birmingham
OL,7,FCity Council said it incurred a
OL,8,F"significant level" of one-off
OL,9,Fresponse and clear-up costs during
OL,10,FApril and May because of the strike.
OL,12,FThey included street cleansing,
OL,13,Fextended opening hours of Mobile
OL,14,FHousehold Waste and Recycling Centres,
OL,15,Fsecurity costs and additional support
OL,16,Fto tackle the accumulation of waste.
OL,18,FThe report also stated that, as the
OL,19,Fstrike continues, additional costs
OL,20,Fwere building up for:
