OL,6,FA proportion of the costs were
OL,7,Fmitigated by the reduction in staff
OL,8,Fcosts, with striking bin workers
OL,9,Finstead being financially supported by
OL,10,Fthe Unite union.
OL,12,FHowever, up to the end of May, the
OL,13,Ffactors were still estimated to have
OL,14,Fcost the council around #3.9 million
OL,15,Faccording to the report.
OL,17,F"It is not possible to determine how
OL,18,Flong the strike action will continue,
OL,19,Fthus a forecast for the future cost
OL,20,Fimpact of the strike has not been
OL,21,Fincorporated," it said.
