OL,6,FIt added that the city council would
OL,7,Fnot be providing a green waste service
OL,8,Fin 2025/26, which had been budgeted to
OL,9,Fachieve #4.4 million.
OL,11,F"Income from bulky waste and
OL,12,Fcommercial waste are also anticipated
OL,13,Fto underachieve," it said.
OL,15,F"However, the income received from the
OL,16,Fenergy contract relating to the
OL,17,Fincineration of waste will over-
OL,18,Fperform and offset this as was seen in
OL,19,F2024/25."
