OL,6,FThe report also focused on the
OL,7,Ftransformation of the council's waste
OL,8,Fservices, which was pushed back
OL,9,Fbecause of the industrial action
OL,10,Fearlier this year.
OL,12,FThe project has been described as a
OL,13,Fkey part of the crisis-hit council's
OL,14,Frecovery plan and will see collections
OL,15,Fmove from weekly to fortnightly.
OL,17,FWeekly food waste collections and a
OL,18,Fsecond recycling bin specifically for
OL,19,Frecycling paper and cardboard were
OL,20,Falso set to be introduced in phases
OL,21,Facross the city from April onwards.
