OL,6,FBut the report said: "The council has
OL,7,Fhad to delay the delivery of several
OL,8,Fsavings and the implementation of
OL,9,Ftransformation plans. It is
OL,10,Fanticipated that as street scene
OL,11,Ftransformation is rolled out, a
OL,12,Fproportion of these savings will be
OL,13,Fachieved but this will be subject to
OL,14,Fthe timing and speed of rollout.
OL,16,F"Some, but not all, of the projected
OL,17,Fsavings shortfall is therefore
OL,18,Fassociated with the impact of the
OL,19,Findustrial action."
