OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FTensions over the strike have dragged
OL,7,Fon into the summer, with Unite voting
OL,8,Fto suspend the membership of Labour
OL,9,Fcouncillors at the city council,
OL,10,Fincluding leader Coun John Cotton and
OL,11,Falso deputy prime minister Angela
OL,12,FRayner.
OL,14,FThe council said it was ending
OL,15,Fnegotiations with Unite to resolve the
OL,16,Fdispute, which was initially triggered
OL,17,Fby the loss of the Waste Recycling and
OL,18,FCollection Officer (WRCO) role.
