OL,6,FStriking workers have raised concerns
OL,7,Fabout pay while the Labour-run
OL,8,Fcouncil's leadership has repeatedly
OL,9,Finsisted a "fair and reasonable" offer
OL,10,Fhad been made.
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council said last week
OL,13,Fit would notify staff and unions of
OL,14,Fits intention to enter consultation
OL,15,Fwith affected workers ` while keeping
OL,16,Fthe door open to those wanting to
OL,17,Faccept offers to retrain or be
OL,18,Fredeployed.
