OL,6,FCouncil leader John Cotton said at the
OL,7,Ftime: "We have negotiated in good
OL,8,Ffaith but, unfortunately, Unite has
OL,9,Frejected all offers so we must now
OL,10,Fpress ahead to both address our equal
OL,11,Fpay risk and make much needed
OL,12,Fimprovements to the waste service.
OL,14,F"This is a service that has not been
OL,15,Fgood enough for a long time and we
OL,16,Fmust improve it.
