OL,6,F"Unite's demands would leave us with
OL,7,Fanother equal pay bill of hundreds of
OL,8,Fmillions of pounds, which is totally
OL,9,Funacceptable, and would jeopardise the
OL,10,Fconsiderable progress we have made in
OL,11,Four financial recovery."
OL,13,FCouncillor Majid Mahmood, Cabinet
OL,14,FMember for Environment, said last week
OL,15,Fthat the council remained committed to
OL,16,Fcreating a "modern, sustainable and
OL,17,Fconsistently reliable waste collection
OL,18,Fservice for all residents".
